==暴雪==
[[雪暴|暴雪]]是此种天气现象带来的最主要的影响。[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]东南部记录到最高{{convert|5|to|18|in}}的降雪。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.clickondetroit.com/blob/view/-/23796294/data/1/-/ltm3g6/-/Snow-totals-Jan-6-2013-pdf.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2014-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107050037/http://www.clickondetroit.com/blob/view/-/23796294/data/1/-/ltm3g6/-/Snow-totals-Jan-6-2013-pdf.pdf |archive-date=2014-01-07 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

降雪量较少的南方如[[田纳西州|田纳西州]]也有{{convert|0.5|and|2|in}}的降雪。<ref name="WTVF">{{cite web|url=http://www.newschannel5.com/story/24360880/dangerously-cold-temperatures-settle-into-mid-state|title=Dangerously Cold Temperatures Settle Into Mid-State|publisher=Nashville News Channel 5|date=January 6, 2014|accessdate=January 6, 2014|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107093743/http://www.newschannel5.com/story/24360880/dangerously-cold-temperatures-settle-into-mid-state|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==低温记录==
报道称2014年1月5日在[[威斯康星州|威斯康星州]][[格林贝_(威斯康星州)|格林贝]]记录到了{{convert|-18|F|C}}的低温，[[美國國家氣象局|美國國家氣象局]]确认那是当时的最低温度，打破了其1979年的记录。<ref name=FOX_DeMarche>{{cite web|last=DeMarche|first=Edmund|title='Polar vortex' set to bring dangerous, record-breaking cold to much of US|url=http://www.foxnews.com/weather/2014/01/04/polar-vortex-to-blast-frigid-air-over-much-us/|work=FoxNews.com|publisher=Fox News|accessdate=January 6, 2014|date=January 4, 2014|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107123023/http://www.foxnews.com/weather/2014/01/04/polar-vortex-to-blast-frigid-air-over-much-us/|dead-url=no}}</ref>1月6日，[[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[奥黑尔國際機場|奥黑尔國際機場]]记录到当日最低温度为 {{convert|-15|F|C}}，打破了1884年记录，并与1988年记录持平。<ref name=NYT_Preston></ref> 

[[温尼伯|温尼伯]]市，在2013年12月31日记录到接近低温记录的{{convert|-36.2|F|C}}，[[风寒指数|风寒指数]]达到{{convert|-54|F|C}}。此时[[北极|北极]]温度仅为{{convert|-20|F|C}}。

==灾害==
此次极地涡旋至少造成13至16人死亡，严寒和糟糕的道路情况是导致这些人遇害的主因。<ref name=FOX_DeMarche></ref><ref name=ABC_Castellano>{{cite news |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/11-died-winter-storm-dumped-feet-snow-northeast/story?id=21407724 |title=At Least 13 Died in Winter Storm That Dumped More Than 2 Feet of Snow Over Northeast |newspaper=ABC News |date=January 3, 2013 |last=Castellano |first=Anthony |accessdate=2014-01-07 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106220059/http://abcnews.go.com/US/11-died-winter-storm-dumped-feet-snow-northeast/story?id=21407724 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]1月5日的[[大停电|大停电]]，造成190,000居民失去电力供应，其造成的影响第二天才恢复。<ref>{{cite web|last=CTVNews.ca Staff|title=Power restored to majority of customers in Newfoundland|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/power-restored-to-majority-of-customers-in-newfoundland-1.1619173|work=CTV News|publisher=Bell Media|accessdate=January 6, 2014|date=January 6, 2014|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107071951/http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/power-restored-to-majority-of-customers-in-newfoundland-1.1619173|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[印地安那州|印地安那州]]、[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]和[[密苏里州|密苏里州]]也有24,000用户失去[[电力|电力]]供应。<ref>[http://www.cnn.com/2014/01/06/us/winter-weather/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 'Historic and life-threatening' freeze brings rare danger warning] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/01/06/us/winter-weather/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |date=20140107113653 }}, CNN, January 6, 2014</ref>

1月5日至6日田纳西州中部降温[[华氏|华氏]]50度，达到{{convert|9|F|C}}，造成的电力系统损害使1,200田纳西用户断电，并使州政府启动了[[应急响应|应急响应]]。<ref name="WTVF"/>

==政府响应==
受影响的区域的学校、道路、政府机构均进行了关闭，上千架次航班也被禁止起飞。

==气候变化==
矛盾的是此次影响北美的极冷天气现象是[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]所导致的。冷空气的路径不寻常地与加拿大[[拉布拉多|拉布拉多]]和[[北冰洋|北冰洋]]区域的异常高温重合<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.climatecentral.org/news/arctic-outbreak-when-the-north-pole-came-to-ohio-16906|title=Arctic Outbreak: When the North Pole Came to Ohio|author=Andrew Freedman|date=2014-01-02|accessdate=2014-01-07|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107131132/http://www.climatecentral.org/news/arctic-outbreak-when-the-north-pole-came-to-ohio-16906|dead-url=no}}</ref>。加拿大东部的[[平流层|平流层]]高温导致极地涡旋向东南而下的道路被堵，因此冷空气直接南下。由於[[北極海|北極海]]的冰層融化，造成區域性的[[反照率|反照率]]降低，氣溫因此提升的更快，出現一種[[正回饋|正回饋]]。由於極地氣溫與其他地區的氣溫差距縮小，以此為動力的[[高速氣流|高速氣流]]可能因此減弱，並造成其路徑變化加大。<ref>{{Citation
